quote><br />\n可以詳細講多少少嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢條唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我反而想知佢會考fashion sense去到幾入"},{"pid":"88360eae6414e3fb700e0b027d54bebc979f2257","tid":217004,"uid":63974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T12:40:15.000Z","msg":"有冇人有Aviva Graduate Program AC?"},{"pid":"e3898064a5143128b372fdc10aa6a576b2b0891f","tid":217004,"uid":20840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:08:48.000Z","msg":"新post lm"},{"pid":"388f111490398f6d1f3ac78c78373b3fd93b3116","tid":217004,"uid":82130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T13:36:58.000Z","msg":"去喱個討論,好似多啲人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/217058/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/217058/page/1</a>"}]}